{"title":"CentOS常用命令及安装应用指令汇总","date":"2023-04-24T04:16:57.453Z","slug":"centos-common-shell-command","comments":true,"tags":["CentOS","Shell脚本","chmod","nodejs","npm","pm2","软链","防火墙"],"updated":"2023-07-18T03:24:56.679Z","content":"<ul>\n<li><h5 id=\"0x00：授权管理\"><a href=\"#0x00：授权管理\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"0x00：授权管理\"></a>0x00：授权管理</h5><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">chmod 777 目录</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>7的由来：读、写、可执行分别代表r、w、x，值分别为4、2、1。</li>\n<li>3个7分别对应文件所有者、群组用户、其他用户的权限值，即4 + 2 + 1 = 7。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><h5 id=\"0x01：安装nodejs和npm\"><a href=\"#0x01：安装nodejs和npm\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"0x01：安装nodejs和npm\"></a>0x01：安装nodejs和npm</h5><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">curl -fsSL https://rpm.nodesource.com/setup_16.x | sudo bash -</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo yum install -y nodejs</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><code>执行后将安装nodejs@16版本</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><h5 id=\"0x02：安装pm2\"><a href=\"#0x02：安装pm2\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"0x02：安装pm2\"></a>0x02：安装pm2</h5><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install -g pm2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><h5 id=\"0x03：pm2运行程序\"><a href=\"#0x03：pm2运行程序\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"0x03：pm2运行程序\"></a>0x03：pm2运行程序</h5><p>进入项目目录后，执行一下命令：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pm2 start npm --name ChatUI -- run start</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><code>start</code>为项目<code>package.json</code>对应的启动指令`</p>\n</li>\n<li><h5 id=\"0x04：添加软链接\"><a href=\"#0x04：添加软链接\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"0x04：添加软链接\"></a>0x04：添加软链接</h5><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ln -s /usr/<span class=\"built_in\">local</span>/nginx/sbin/nginx /usr/bin/nginx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><code>/usr/local/nginx/sbin/nginx</code>为对应的真实路径，<code>/usr/bin/nginx</code>为软链接位置。</p>\n</li>\n<li><h5 id=\"0x05：防火墙管理\"><a href=\"#0x05：防火墙管理\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"0x05：防火墙管理\"></a>0x05：防火墙管理</h5><ul>\n<li><p>禁用防火墙</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">systemctl <span class=\"built_in\">disable</span> firewalld</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>启用防火墙</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">systemctl <span class=\"built_in\">enable</span> firewalld</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>开启防火墙</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">systemctl start firewalld</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>停止防火墙</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">systemctl stop firewalld</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>查看防火墙状态</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">systemctl status firewalld</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n","next":{"title":"基于HLS协议的在线直播流测试地址[1050个](更新时间:2023-04-23)","slug":"hls-test-url"},"link":"https://www.alipay.one/post/centos-common-shell-command/"}